(6)Spanish Society of Medical Oncology (SEOM) Oncogeriatrics Section, Reina 
Sofía University Hospital. Instituto Maimónides de Investigación Biomédica de 
Córdoba (IMIBIC), Córdoba, Spain.
(7)Spanish Society of Medical Oncology (SEOM) Oncogeriatrics Section, Ramón y 
Cajal University Hospital, Madrid, Spain.
(8)Spanish Society of Medical Oncology (SEOM) Oncogeriatrics Section, Virgen de 
