209. Nat Commun. 2023 Jul 27;14(1):4518. doi: 10.1038/s41467-023-40245-6.

Increasing number of long-lived ancestors marks a decade of healthspan extension 
and healthier metabolomics profiles.

van den Berg N(1)(2), Rodríguez-Girondo M(3), van Dijk IK(4), Slagboom 
